# Add daemon and session tests for startup replay ordering and successful row deletion

## Requirements

- Add restart-oriented tests that prove startup replay behavior instead of only low-level queue API tests.
- Cover ordering, deletion on success, and interaction with pending agent resume.
- Exercise the session runtime rather than relying solely on mocked queue-state assertions.

## Acceptance Criteria

- Tests prove startup replay drains queued rows in the intended order.
- Tests prove successful replay deletes the durable queue rows.
- Tests prove pending agent resume still precedes durable inbound replay when both kinds of work exist.
